Memoization

- Make the brute force solution

  - Visualize the problem as a tree
  - Implement the tree using recursion
  - Test it (should be able to give a solution with valid results)

- Make it Efficient

  - Add a memo object as a default parameter
    - Using a default parameter will allow us to create a new object upon function call and use the same memo throughout recursion
  - Add a base case to return memo values
  - Store return values into the memo
